					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9487226#post-4094036</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9487226/scp-2801#post-4094036</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Thu, 20 Dec 2018 21:10:29 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Attila the Pun</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1685633</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Ladies, gentlemen, and eldritch horrors, the SCP-2801 rewrite is finally here! Now with more actually-relevent description!</p> <p>The old one had been sitting at +7 for about 3 months, but it was such a mess that I basically rewrote this thing from the ground up. While the core anomaly is basically unchanged, Neurocrack was changed to SCP-2801 while the variants were moved to -1, the description was made clearer, technobabble was cut down on (as much as I could manage without changing the core anomaly), a completely new story was written, and Snyder received a character overhaul. While this one is about 1,000 words shorter than the original, I think it works a lot better.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=455145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Petrograd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=455145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" >Petrograd</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncannyon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4374851&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Uncannyon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4374851)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncannyon" >Uncannyon</a></span> for help with brainstorming.<br /> Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3489662&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="mayoculpa" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3489662)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mayoculpa" >mayoculpa</a></span>, Roboticon in chat, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lord-of-laugh" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2916583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Lord_of_Laugh" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2916583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lord-of-laugh" >Lord_of_Laugh</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jabyrwock" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2300057&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="jabyrwock" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2300057)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jabyrwock" >jabyrwock</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smooothcriminal" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4194278&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Smooothcriminal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4194278)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/smooothcriminal" >Smooothcriminal</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ensophos" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1676981&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Ensophos" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1676981)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ensophos" >Ensophos</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=455145&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="Petrograd" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=455145)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/petrograd" >Petrograd</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" >not_a_seagull</a></span> for crit!<br /> And finally, special thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drdromeus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3785128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1545340264" alt="DrDromeus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3785128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drdromeus" >DrDromeus</a></span> for moral support!</p> 
